name: CreateGAVotersTablePG
rule:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "Georgia"."Voters" (
	"CountyCode" varchar(3) NOT NULL,
	"RegistrationNbr" varchar(8) NOT NULL,
	"VoterStatus" varchar(1),
	"VoterLastName" varchar(20),
	"VoterFirstName" varchar(20),
	"VoterMiddleMaiden" varchar(20),
	"VoterNameSuffix" varchar(3),
	"VoterNameTitle" varchar(3),
	"ResHouseNbr" varchar(6),
	"ResStreetName" varchar(30),
	"ResStreetSuffix" varchar(2),
	"ResAptUnitNbr" varchar(8),
	"ResCityName" varchar(17),
	"ResZip" varchar(5),
	"ResZipPlus4" varchar(4),
	"MidrFlag" varchar(1),
	"PollWorker" varchar(1),
	"TransactionCode" varchar(1),
	"TransactionYearMonth" varchar(6),
	"Filler1" varchar(2),
	"DateOfBirth" date,
	"RegistrationDate" date,
	"Race" varchar(1),
	"Gender" varchar(1),
	"Absentee" varchar(1),
	"LandDistrict" varchar(3),
	"LandLot" varchar(4),
	"OriginalRegDate" date,
	"StatusReason" varchar(9),
	"Filler2" varchar(5),
	"CountyPrecinctId" varchar(5),
	"CityPrecinctId" varchar(5),
	"CongressionalDistrict" varchar(3),
	"SenateDistrict" varchar(3),
	"HouseDistrict" varchar(3),
	"JudicialDistrict" varchar(3),
	"CommDistrict" varchar(3),
	"SchoolDistrict" varchar(3),
	"CountyDistAName" varchar(13),
	"CountyDistAValue" varchar(3),
	"CountyDistBName" varchar(13),
	"CountyDistBValue" varchar(3),
	"MunicipalName" varchar(17),
	"MunicipalCode" varchar(3),
	"WardCityCouncilName" varchar(13),
	"WardCityCouncil" varchar(3),
	"CitySchoolDistName" varchar(13),
	"CitySchoolDist" varchar(3),
	"CityDistAName" varchar(13),
	"CityDistAValue" varchar(3),
	"CityDistBName" varchar(13),
	"CityDistBValue" varchar(3),
	"CityDistCName" varchar(13),
	"CityDistCValue" varchar(3),
	"CityDistDName" varchar(13),
	"CityDistDValue" varchar(3),
	"DateLastVotedDate" date,
	"TypeOfElection" varchar(3),
	"PartyLastVoted" varchar(1),
	"LastContactDate" date,
	"MailHouseNbr" varchar(6),
	"MailStreetName" varchar(30),
	"MailStreetSuffix" varchar(2),
	"MailAptUnitNbr" varchar(8),
	"MailCity" varchar(17),
	"MailState" varchar(2),
	"MailZip" varchar(5),
	"MailZipPlus4" varchar(4),
	"Filler3" varchar(2),
	"MailAddress2" varchar(30),
	"MailAddress3" varchar(30),
	"MailCounty" varchar(20),
	"DateAdded" date,
	"DateChanged" date,
	"DistrictCombo" varchar(3),
	"ResBuilding" varchar(3),
	"MailRRPOBox" varchar(8),
	"CombinedStreetAddr" varchar(60),
	"ExportDate" date NOT NULL,
	CONSTRAINT "Voters_pkey" PRIMARY KEY ("CountyCode", "RegistrationNbr", "ExportDate")
)
WITH (OIDS=FALSE)
